{"tid":1507063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［國際文宣］91機場要預先對外國文宣","createTime":"2019-08-26T04:13:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T11:15:18.000Z","uid":65888,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ccc9178b4afef33a24c10385414fb179872effbb","tid":1507063,"uid":65888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:13:10.000Z","msg":"上次經驗之後，我地今次要比定足夠時間人地改機票又好乜都好，最重要係要預先傳到出去。<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲翻譯唔同語言文宣圖，我地一齊係reddit, twitter度推。"},{"pid":"2087a6aefdfbc766a45e5675400c1b75ff8e9739","tid":1507063,"uid":29899,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:21:20.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 文宣集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505474</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogleDrive: 91機場文宣資源 (手足有新貨話我知，會Upload上去)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY8orGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=6cb6e186\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#黑警還眼 #612 #721 #811 #823</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#推到有英文文宣#</span></strong></span><br />\n----------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>英文文宣建議：</strong></span><br />\n內容:<br />\n91 Hong Kong International Airport<br />\nSOS: Humanitarian Crisis Alert<br />\nGovernment has failed us. Police shot us.<br />\nIt&rsquo;s now or never, please stand with HK.<br />\nThanks in advance for your support and understanding.<br />\n<br />\n方向/ 建議：<br />\n-強調事態之緊急及嚴重<br />\n-形式係事先通知，而非道歉，機場示威是出師有名同埋其中既正當性<br />\n-例如可用&rdquo;SOS&rdquo;之字眼<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rt9LBCx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frt9LBCx.jpg&h=73c530e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3kZESP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3kZESP.jpg&h=ba0a90fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7wVcXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7wVcXg.jpg&h=05fc61c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLLrqSL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLLrqSL.jpg&h=724c5863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyFriWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyFriWu.jpg&h=47e393ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00f1f498c84d6f2eed82f093bd317a0b836fc0f3","tid":1507063,"uid":65888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:28:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ef74de3df45190494ab5570ee0f1106aa3c643e0","tid":1507063,"uid":65888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:30:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"17f80cc7bcd970dc57a6604ef13e4f9eee679d50","tid":1507063,"uid":103102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:32:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8b3db9fe256b2505711728bfca8d669413787c3a","tid":1507063,"uid":29899,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:33:28.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n英文文宣建議：<br />\n內容:<br />\n91 Hong Kong International Airport<br />\nSOS: Humanitarian Crisis Alert<br />\nGovernment has failed us. Police shot us.<br />\nIt&rsquo;s now or never, please stand with HK.<br />\nThanks in advance for your support and understanding.<br />\n<br />\n方向/ 建議：<br />\n-強調事態之緊急及嚴重<br />\n-形式係事先通知，而非道歉，機場示威是出師有名同埋其中既正當性<br />\n-例如可用&rdquo;SOS&rdquo;之字眼"},{"pid":"4bc0ca0d365f4c1c01cd885abe95bef8074b78fe","tid":1507063,"uid":51924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re